MAGIC LORE NO DROP<br>
Slot: CHARM<br>
Wt: 0.5 Size: TINY<br>
Class: ALL<br>
Race: ALL<br>
<br>
Item Information:<br>
Grants a bonus if you are using any kind of bane weapon<br>
<br>
Zone: Gulf of Guntak (village outside troll fort)<br>
Mob: a dastardly scoundrel<br>
Location: n2300 n300 (spawns inside the hut)<br>
<br>
Sorry, no info on what stats it gives since bards aren't known for being bane weapon users most of the time, but might interest you meatshield types. Will get some crap bane weapon and let you guys know.<br>
<br>
Impresario Cypris Edge<br>
Maestro of Bristlebane.<br>
Part of the few, the proud, the Warrior Poets!<br>
