<br>
MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP<br>
Slot: Charm<br>
STR: +10 MANA: +15<br>
Focus: Extended Range II<br>
WT: 0.1 Size: SMALL<br>
Class: ALL<br>
Race: ALL<br>
<br>
Item Info: Improves as your dexterity increases. May gain an effect at high levels.<br>
<br>
