<br>
Allakhazam spoiler thread - <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=2320">everquest.allakhazam.com/...quest=2320</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
